Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to any other activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' when followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before reaching 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call' across variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with 'High' impact versus 'Medium' or 'Low' impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' within the top 10 most frequent process variants
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' within the least frequent process variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + In Progress' across different organizations (grouped by 'organization country')
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases involving 'PROD582' product
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for all cases in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases exceeding the overall average duration of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in the fastest case to reach 'Completed + Closed' from event log start
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
